# Shell scripts

Read [AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md). Skill: `.cursor/skills/new-bootstrap-module/`.

- Bash 3.2+ only — no bash 4+ syntax
- Logic inside functions; scripts are sourced by `bootstrap.sh`
- Use helpers from `scripts/helpers.sh` — no new YAML parsers
- Install targets from `config/*.yaml` only
- Idempotency checks + `DRY_RUN` support on every install/configure path
- Finish with `make test && make lint`
